    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Zebronics",
    "description": "Grow your career with Zebronics! We are hiring a SEO Specialist for our Gwalior team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Zebronics:\nZebronics is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zebronics!",
